# Personal  Task Management  â€“ Full Stack 

This is a complete full-stack Task Management System where users can create an account, log in securely, and manage their personal tasks.

Each user can:

* Add tasks
* Edit tasks
* Delete tasks
* Mark tasks as completed
* Log out securely

All tasks are private and belong only to the logged-in user.

---

# Technologies Used

# Backend

* Node.js
* TypeScript
* Express
* Prisma ORM
* SQLite Database
* JWT Authentication
* bcrypt for password encryption

# Frontend

* Next.js (App Router)
* React
* TypeScript

