# Running the Project Locally

# Backend Setup


cd backend
npm install
npx prisma migrate dev
npm run dev


Backend runs on:
[http://localhost:4000](http://localhost:4000)



# Frontend Setup


cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev


Frontend runs on:
[http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)



# User Registration (Create Account)

1. Open the app in browser
2. Click Register / Create Account
3. Enter email and password
4. Click Sign Up
5. You will be redirected to Login page



# User Login

1. Enter registered email and password
2. Click Login
3. You will be redirected to Dashboard

JWT token is stored for secure API access.



# Dashboard â€“ Task Management

# Add Task

Type task name â†’ Click Add

# Edit Task

Click Edit â†’ Modify text â†’ Click Save

# Delete Task

Click Delete â†’ Task removed

#  Toggle Completion

Click Done to complete
Click Undo to revert

#  Logout

Click Logout to end session



#  API Endpoints

# Auth

POST /auth/register
POST /auth/login

# Tasks

GET /tasks
POST /tasks
PATCH /tasks/:id
DELETE /tasks/:id
PATCH /tasks/:id/toggle

